---
import DefaultLayout from '../layouts/DefaultLayout.astro'
import Hero from '../components/Hero.astro'
import { Icon } from 'astro-icon/components'
import Feature from '../components/Feature.astro'
import Counter from '../components/Counter.astro'
import ContentMedia from '../components/ContentMedia.astro'
import { Accordion, AccordionItem } from 'accessible-astro-components'
import Testimonial from '../components/Testimonial.astro'
---

<DefaultLayout title="Home">
  <Hero />
  <section class="my-36">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="mb-16">How I can help</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-12 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
        <Feature name="workflow" title="Workflow optimisation">
          I can take a look at your current processes and identify any bottlenecks, double-handling and opportunities to
          streamline, automate or delegate so you can get some time back in your day.
        </Feature>
        <Feature name="screen-code" title="System setup">
          If you're looking to implement a new tool in your business (such as a CRM) but are feeling a bit overwhelmed
          by the technical side of it or just don't have the time to set it up, I can do it for you or with you.
        </Feature>
        <Feature name="lightning" title="Automation">
          Spend less time on repetitive tasks by automating using native automation features in your existing tools, or
          connecting with third-party tools like Make or Zapier.
        </Feature>
        <Feature name="books" title="Documentation">
          Do your processes only exist in your head? I'll help you lighten the mental load by creating a set of
          lightweight guides that document what you do, how you do it, and when to take action.
        </Feature>
        <Feature name="canvas" title="Training">
          If you're struggling to use some of your existing tools or feel like you could be getting more out of them if
          you knew a bit more. I have experience with Notion, Asana, Squarespace, Google Workspace, Kajabi, Zapier,
          Make, Sprout Studio and more.
        </Feature>
        <Feature name="checkboxes" title="Getting things done">
          If you can never seem to get on top of your to-do list, let me take some of the load. Whether it's website
          updates, file storage, inbox management, document creation, email campaigns or other support for your
          day-to-day operations, I've got you. I cover all this in my VA (virtual assistant) support packages.
        </Feature>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="my-36">
    <div class="container grid grid-cols-1 gap-24 md:grid-cols-3">
      <div class="col-span-1">
        <img class="lg:block" src="/lc-headshot-apr2025.jpg" alt="Lauren Champs" decoding="async" />
      </div>
      <div class="col-span-2 flex flex-col items-start gap-4">
        <h2>About Me</h2>
        <p class="text-2xl">
          I am a logical thinker who loves nothing more than tackling a problem and coming up with a fix.
        </p>
        <p>
          I love helping purpose-led business owners... I'm a generalist at heart, always exploring new tools and
          learning new skills. It's this nature that means I thrive getting to know you and your unique business, and
          looking for solutions that will work for you.
        </p>
        <p>
          Before starting out on my own, I spent over a decade in the higher education sector, from student support to
          working with research systems and databases to creating websites. The common thread through all my work has
          been a desire to make digital solutions simpler for the people who use them.
        </p>
        <a class="button has-icon" href="/about#qualifications"
          >See my qualifications
          <Icon name="arrow-right" />
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

